# Product Requirements Document (PRD)

# Project Name

**CineVerse** – A Premium Movie & TV Streaming Platform

---

# Version

1.0

# Product Owner

Product Team

# Goal

Develop a modern, high-performance OTT streaming platform inspired by Netflix while featuring a unique premium visual identity. The platform should provide a seamless movie discovery and streaming experience with responsive design, smooth animations, and personalized recommendations.

---

# Vision

Create a cinematic streaming platform that combines the best user experience from Netflix, Disney+, and Apple TV+ while introducing a fresh glassmorphism-inspired interface and intelligent content discovery.

---

# Objectives

## Business Objectives

* Build a scalable streaming platform.
* Deliver an engaging user experience.
* Increase user retention through personalization.
* Support future subscription models.
* Enable content management through an admin dashboard.

---

